Swipe ➡️ for before!! Well today didn’t go quite as planned! I planned on hitting up Target, grabbing a pinkity drinkity, and getting items to share how to style a bathroom…..but my son Landon had other plans!! His left side started hurting really bad, it did this about a week ago too, so I took him to the dr. They said it might be a kidney stone, which is crazy, because he’s only 13! So now we’re waiting to be seen at the ER. We are on hour three of waiting 🤦🏼‍♀️🤦🏼‍♀️ Hoping to be seen soon!!! So thought I’d a share bathroom styling pic while we wait! Can you believe what my bathroom originally looked like!! The tub took up half the bath! Have you had kidney stones before??? I hear they are so incredibly painful!
